### Fetch all teams in the league
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/league
Accept: application/json

### Fetch a specific team by ID
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/NY
Accept: application/json

### Fetch team - not found
GET http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/INVALID
Accept: application/json

### Add player to team — paste the id of a newly created (unassigned) player
POST http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/NY/paste-created-player-id-here
Accept: application/json

### Add player to team — 409 (seed player already on a team)
POST http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/NY/330eb324-3382-4fca-b20e-2b4c7e278047
Accept: application/json

### Add player to team — 404 (team not found)
POST http://{{host}}{{basePath}}/v1/team/INVALID/330eb324-3382-4fca-b20e-2b4c7e278047
Accept: application/json
